platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Learn to build and manage a towering skyscraper.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: What are those towers that touch the sky? Tinybops awesome sandbox teaches kids the fun wayby letting them build, watch, and play. As they add floors and test the effects of plumbing problems and earthquakes, they're actually learning basic design and engineering principles. Amazing details aboundfrom all the busy little inhabitants to the full-blown skyline you can make.
